::DarkMouse/KitKat::

DarkMouse::
She turned and looked at Wildfire.  then her optics got wide and she 
dropped the tray. "Oh my gosh. KitKat is out there."
She ran to the console. "KitKat, get back to base! Now!"


KitKat::
She heard Darkmouse on her link. "No Way. I'm here at the cave and 
looking for Rowdy. I'm not coming back without him."
She transformed into bot mode.
"Rowdy? If your here, answer me darn it! Rowdy?"
